formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
> As per the information and explanation given and records & documents provided to me by the partners of the firm, the partnership firm has borrowed monies from various persons for development of the various projects of the firm. Unsecured loans have not been borrowed for any specific project and it is a general loan for all the projects carried out by partnership firm and hence it is not possible for me to bifurcate these borrowed amount to a specific project and hence the amount of loans shown here above are the total borrowings for all the projects of the partnership firm. The partnership firm does not have any outstanding loan from Banks or Financial Institutions for development of the above mentioned project.					
> The partnership firm has received the total Booking amount of Rs. 5,72,,40,000/- up to 28.02.2022 and 70% of same amounting to Rs. 4,00,68,000/- should have been deposited to RERA retension account but out of same only amounting to Rs. 2,40,94,700/- have been deposited into RERA account. Hence here above in point no. 7 Amount withdrawn till date of this certificate as per the Books of Accounts and Bank Statement is considered as 70% of the total boking amount received at Rs. 2,02,76,900/- up to 31st December, 21 plus amount received and sposited in RERA account from 1st January 2022 to 28th February 2022.					
> The partnership firm has not made agreement to sale in some of the units where more than 10% of the final sale amount has been received by them. Whereas in some of the units where the whole amount has been received as single payment at time of execution of sale deed and hence no agreement to sale has been made in those cases and the date mentioned in Form-3A is the sale deed date.					
> In case of some plots for which sale deed has already been executed but against which no amount has been received. Where no amount have been received against booked units for which sale deed also have been executed, we have shown Rs.1 as token amount received to avoid any technical error while submitting form-3 online.
